IN RE: Charles HOLLENBACK No. 480P12-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 1, 2018 Mr. Charles Hollenback, for Hollenback, Charles Mr. Joseph L. Hyde, Raleigh, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina Mr. William R. West, District Attorney, for State

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Petitioner on the 18th of December 2017 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Cumberland County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 1st of March 2018."
